WEBVTT

01:53.170 --> 01:57.560
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.840 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 8]

02:05.470 --> 02:06.670
Young Master Qiyan,

02:06.690 --> 02:08.620
what do you want to talk to us about?

02:09.470 --> 02:10.560
Rumor has it

02:10.560 --> 02:12.470
that Lord Zheng has been plagued
by nightmares recently.

02:12.470 --> 02:13.730
I happen to have a plan.

02:16.030 --> 02:17.430
He happens to have a plan?

02:19.350 --> 02:20.350
What kind of plan?

02:20.400 --> 02:21.120
Tell us.

02:21.620 --> 02:23.079
Stop being so mysterious.

02:24.470 --> 02:25.190
After all,

02:25.440 --> 02:27.240
helping us is helping yourself.

02:27.490 --> 02:28.490
Am I right,

02:29.110 --> 02:30.640
Second Young Master Zheng?

02:34.850 --> 02:36.410
Second Young Master Zheng?

02:38.440 --> 02:39.440
What do you mean?

02:39.770 --> 02:41.210
That day at Huan'e House,

02:41.230 --> 02:43.540
you stole the fabric pattern
from my clothes for him.

02:43.540 --> 02:44.579
Remember?

02:49.670 --> 02:51.670
So Young Master Lou Qiyan

02:51.720 --> 02:54.240
turns out to be
Second Young Master Zheng Shi.

02:54.240 --> 02:57.560
You and Mr. Zheng share a deep bond
as grandparent and grandchild.

02:57.560 --> 02:59.079
Meeting you here today,

02:59.890 --> 03:01.430
I presume you are also looking for

03:01.430 --> 03:04.490
the old ancestral temple
from Mr. Zheng's nightmares.

03:05.130 --> 03:08.260
You're not as ignorant
of worldly affairs as rumors say.

03:08.970 --> 03:11.380
I do want to repair the ancestral temple

03:11.500 --> 03:14.100
to bring some comfort
to Grandfather's heart.

03:17.170 --> 03:18.240
So you are

03:18.920 --> 03:22.710
looking for the ancestral temple
that the Zheng family wants to repair.

03:22.710 --> 03:23.570
I remember

03:23.680 --> 03:25.240
the late governor Qi Hua,

03:25.240 --> 03:28.190
to commemorate those meritorious officials
who died in battle,

03:28.190 --> 03:29.090
specially ordered

03:29.090 --> 03:30.890
the construction of the temple.

03:31.410 --> 03:32.850
But

03:33.000 --> 03:34.240
hasn't the temple

03:34.240 --> 03:35.750
been lost due to the succession war

03:35.750 --> 03:37.120
for a long time?

03:37.660 --> 03:39.720
Not only do I know the exact location,

03:40.140 --> 03:43.200
but I also have
the original construction blueprints.

03:46.329 --> 03:47.220
Tell me.

03:47.970 --> 03:49.430
What are your conditions?

03:51.850 --> 03:52.570
Why?

03:53.120 --> 03:55.920
You're brave enough
to negotiate conditions now?

03:58.870 --> 03:59.520
Yeah.

03:59.720 --> 04:01.130
Tell us your conditions.

04:01.160 --> 04:02.620
How much money do you want?

04:02.850 --> 04:04.710
This has nothing to do with money.

04:06.910 --> 04:08.470
Then...

04:10.840 --> 04:12.140
Second Young Master Zheng,

04:12.140 --> 04:13.680
you are afraid that giving us
the blueprints

04:13.680 --> 04:15.010
will offend Lord Zheng?

04:16.810 --> 04:20.610
I've never been much concerned
with political and worldly affairs.

04:22.029 --> 04:24.430
You're not afraid of trouble,
and you don't lack money.

04:24.430 --> 04:25.630
Then what do you want?

04:27.250 --> 04:28.890
If you want the map and blueprints,

04:28.890 --> 04:30.090
I can give them to you.

04:30.640 --> 04:31.190
Moreover,

04:31.190 --> 04:33.110
the ancestral temple covers a large area.

04:33.110 --> 04:33.900
Repairing it

04:33.920 --> 04:36.010
will cost a considerable amount of money.

04:36.010 --> 04:37.200
My Juyun Pavilion

04:37.220 --> 04:39.150
is willing to bear half of the cost.

04:41.780 --> 04:43.190
Bear half of the cost?

04:43.510 --> 04:45.710
Do you think I can't afford to repair it?

04:46.000 --> 04:47.040
If you ask me,

04:47.240 --> 04:48.430
you know very well

04:48.430 --> 04:50.830
how important the temple is to Mr. Zheng.

04:51.330 --> 04:53.060
Yet you are handing it over now.

04:53.920 --> 04:55.650
What are your true intentions?

05:00.360 --> 05:01.360
Your Excellency.

05:01.870 --> 05:02.870
Your Excellency.

05:03.310 --> 05:05.020
We are short of money everywhere
in the residence right now.

05:05.020 --> 05:06.680
We should save wherever we can.

05:06.680 --> 05:07.400
Besides,

05:08.020 --> 05:09.170
Juyun Pavilion

05:09.200 --> 05:09.910
has plenty of manpower

05:09.910 --> 05:10.740
and complete materials.

05:10.740 --> 05:11.980
Why not go for it?

05:15.260 --> 05:16.780
I do have one condition.

05:17.270 --> 05:18.190
What is it?

05:24.040 --> 05:25.000
I see.

05:25.630 --> 05:27.600
I'll play a tune for you when I get back.

05:27.600 --> 05:28.160
You...

05:32.230 --> 05:33.760
It's been a few days. You...

05:36.350 --> 05:38.790
Your Ladyship, you've become
even more amusing.

05:38.790 --> 05:39.650
How about this?

05:40.600 --> 05:41.659
You teach me a tune.

05:41.820 --> 05:43.110
When I master it,

05:43.140 --> 05:44.470
I'll give you the items.

05:44.700 --> 05:45.740
What do you think?

05:45.770 --> 05:46.650
Okay.

05:46.670 --> 05:47.720
-Let's do—
-No.

05:48.390 --> 05:49.430
Of course not.

05:50.090 --> 05:51.490
This is highly improper.

05:54.630 --> 05:55.680
Your Excellency.

05:55.990 --> 05:57.110
Why not?

05:58.070 --> 05:59.500
She's best at teaching.

05:59.840 --> 06:00.520
You should know this

06:00.520 --> 06:02.110
better than anyone else.

06:02.860 --> 06:04.540
Fan Yun is my wife now.

06:05.190 --> 06:07.470
I'm sure you know this better than anyone.

06:07.470 --> 06:08.110
Besides,

06:08.970 --> 06:10.730
your problem is fundamental.

06:11.190 --> 06:13.120
It doesn't matter who teaches you.

06:17.020 --> 06:19.050
Dripping water can hollow out stone.

06:19.050 --> 06:20.160
Given time,

06:20.190 --> 06:22.240
there will definitely be improvement.

06:22.240 --> 06:23.040
Enough.

06:23.600 --> 06:25.200
Give us the items if you want.

06:25.330 --> 06:26.090
If you don't,

06:26.120 --> 06:27.320
don't waste our time.

06:27.340 --> 06:28.340
My Lady, let's go.

06:28.680 --> 06:29.480
Let's discuss it again.

06:29.480 --> 06:31.720
You can keep looking for them yourselves

06:31.720 --> 06:33.250
and then fix it yourselves.

06:33.920 --> 06:35.240
But as to the time...

06:36.260 --> 06:36.900
Right.

06:36.950 --> 06:37.560
Then why not...

06:37.560 --> 06:38.120
This...

06:39.350 --> 06:40.350
Your Excellency.

06:40.950 --> 06:41.800
Second Young Master Zheng,

06:41.800 --> 06:43.120
let us go back and think about it.

06:43.120 --> 06:44.190
Wait for our word.

06:44.190 --> 06:45.390
We'll think about it.

06:46.200 --> 06:47.640
Your Excellency.

07:18.860 --> 07:20.460
Did you find the blueprints?

07:20.600 --> 07:21.430
No.

07:22.150 --> 07:24.080
Then what were you thinking about?

07:24.610 --> 07:25.900
I was thinking about

07:25.930 --> 07:27.280
Lou Qiyan.

07:27.300 --> 07:27.980
No,

07:28.150 --> 07:29.590
strictly speaking,

07:29.610 --> 07:31.410
it's Second Young Master Zheng.

07:34.630 --> 07:36.690
Why were you thinking about that guy?

07:37.950 --> 07:38.950
Your Excellency.

07:39.310 --> 07:40.120
Lou Qiyan

07:40.120 --> 07:42.230
is Zheng Shi, the Second Young Master
of the Zheng family.

07:42.230 --> 07:43.830
Aren't you surprised at all?

07:44.950 --> 07:45.830
I'm surprised.

07:46.580 --> 07:48.440
No matter what identity he takes,

07:49.430 --> 07:50.720
I find him annoying.

07:51.240 --> 07:53.570
The blueprints were right there just now,

07:53.580 --> 07:54.980
but you didn't want them.

07:55.159 --> 07:56.680
Now we can't find them.

07:58.040 --> 07:59.159
What should we do?

08:00.120 --> 08:01.210
I don't believe it.

08:01.540 --> 08:02.910
I am a genius.

08:02.930 --> 08:04.290
In such a small library,

08:04.320 --> 08:05.980
how can I not find a blueprint?

08:17.320 --> 08:18.900
My goodness.

08:19.290 --> 08:20.970
Still can't find them.

08:31.640 --> 08:32.640
What should we do?

08:35.510 --> 08:36.770
Keep looking for them.

08:40.059 --> 08:41.659
I can't do it anymore.

08:51.380 --> 08:52.380
Heading out?

08:54.720 --> 08:55.720
Your Excellency.

08:56.990 --> 08:58.620
Why are you

08:58.650 --> 08:59.830
here?

09:00.240 --> 09:01.320
I knew it.

09:04.720 --> 09:06.780
You are brilliant, Your Excellency.

09:08.250 --> 09:09.450
I don't want you to go.

09:09.900 --> 09:11.430
Your Excellency, trust me.

09:11.560 --> 09:12.210
One day.

09:12.890 --> 09:14.190
I can get it done in one day.

09:14.190 --> 09:15.670
I trust you,

09:16.350 --> 09:17.590
but I don't trust him.

09:17.980 --> 09:19.000
Why?

09:19.230 --> 09:20.740
Your Excellency, think about it.

09:20.740 --> 09:22.400
Not only is he giving us the blueprints,

09:22.400 --> 09:24.030
but he's also giving us money.

09:24.030 --> 09:25.820
What a great deal!

09:26.120 --> 09:26.720
You...

09:28.750 --> 09:29.360
Just...

09:31.460 --> 09:32.340
Just this once.

09:34.010 --> 09:34.710
Once.

09:34.860 --> 09:35.680
Just this once.

09:35.680 --> 09:37.280
No physical contact.

09:37.390 --> 09:38.440
No joking around.

09:38.440 --> 09:39.900
No staying out overnight.

09:41.310 --> 09:42.090
No matter how hot it is,

09:42.090 --> 09:43.870
you can't take off your clothes.

09:43.870 --> 09:45.150
Take off...

09:45.170 --> 09:46.170
take off clothes?

09:47.470 --> 09:49.140
What are you talking about?

09:49.520 --> 09:51.280
So childish.

09:52.030 --> 09:52.890
Promise me now.

09:53.360 --> 09:54.750
I-I promise you.

09:55.150 --> 09:56.150
Then...

09:56.170 --> 09:57.600
I have the carriage ready.

09:57.600 --> 09:59.060
I'll wait for your return.

10:01.960 --> 10:03.030
Thank you, Your Excellency.

10:03.030 --> 10:03.870
Don't worry, Your Excellency.

10:03.870 --> 10:06.200
I'll complete the mission successfully.

10:06.990 --> 10:07.940
I'm leaving now.

10:08.330 --> 10:09.930
Thank you, Your Excellency.

10:11.990 --> 10:12.870
Slow down.

10:13.200 --> 10:14.320
Don't worry!

10:18.760 --> 10:21.800
[Huan'e House]

10:20.470 --> 10:21.760
Before this,

10:22.070 --> 10:23.730
have you ever hired a teacher?

10:25.120 --> 10:26.670
They were all mediocre.

10:28.410 --> 10:29.290
Then why not

10:29.320 --> 10:30.320
play a piece

10:30.340 --> 10:31.270
for me to hear?

10:33.550 --> 10:34.270
Sure.

10:34.810 --> 10:36.210
Since you are my teacher,

10:36.530 --> 10:37.960
I will be honest with you.

11:05.600 --> 11:06.240
How was it?

11:09.630 --> 11:11.180
W-What do you mean?

11:12.030 --> 11:12.870
My technique.

11:18.550 --> 11:21.010
And the emotion
flowing from my fingertips?

11:24.800 --> 11:27.440
Emotion?

11:29.870 --> 11:31.780
A teacher once told me that

11:32.760 --> 11:34.560
my legato is steady and solid,

11:34.590 --> 11:36.320
my vibrato is like shaking jade
and pearls,

11:36.320 --> 11:38.580
and my glissando is exquisite and light.

11:40.510 --> 11:42.510
What kind of teacher

11:43.050 --> 11:45.010
could give such a review?

11:46.320 --> 11:47.290
This must have...

11:47.290 --> 11:48.570
cost a lot.

11:52.280 --> 11:53.490
A thousand gold a day.

11:53.600 --> 11:54.600
What?

11:55.030 --> 11:56.550
A thousand gold a day?

11:58.240 --> 11:59.360
I understand.

11:59.380 --> 12:01.100
Then that makes sense.

12:02.120 --> 12:03.180
It makes sense now.

12:04.120 --> 12:05.120
To be honest,

12:05.570 --> 12:07.320
the tones I've heard since childhood

12:07.320 --> 12:09.010
seem to differ from others

12:09.670 --> 12:10.870
just slightly.

12:11.270 --> 12:12.600
Almost all the teachers

12:12.600 --> 12:14.060
advised me to give up early

12:14.240 --> 12:15.440
and stop struggling.

12:16.800 --> 12:18.080
Do you think someone like me

12:18.080 --> 12:20.130
can still play a decent tune?

12:20.870 --> 12:22.420
So that's how it is.

12:23.340 --> 12:24.470
Young Master Qiyan,

12:24.680 --> 12:26.080
I was impolite just now.

12:26.740 --> 12:27.600
How about this?

12:28.650 --> 12:29.770
Let me think of

12:29.800 --> 12:31.010
a way to help you.

12:34.070 --> 12:36.240
So what exactly are you thinking,
Your Excellency?

12:36.240 --> 12:37.270
Dark Wolf...

12:40.170 --> 12:41.200
Sit down and talk!

12:45.960 --> 12:47.120
This is precisely because Mr. Zheng

12:47.120 --> 12:48.780
targeted Fan Yun everywhere.

12:49.080 --> 12:49.870
In order to let Fan Yun

12:49.870 --> 12:52.200
gain recognition among the major nobles,

12:52.420 --> 12:54.060
I had to act this way.

12:54.460 --> 12:55.490
If you must mention

12:55.490 --> 12:57.110
the matter of feigning illness,

12:57.110 --> 12:58.630
you can understand it

12:58.650 --> 13:00.450
as walking on the edge of a cliff.

13:00.630 --> 13:01.980
But it can also be understood

13:01.980 --> 13:04.440
as enjoying the unique scenery
from the top.

13:05.240 --> 13:06.640
As for the repair work,

13:06.660 --> 13:07.790
I actually think

13:07.820 --> 13:09.450
Fan Yun must do it

13:09.490 --> 13:11.100
and do it beautifully.

13:11.550 --> 13:12.320
In this way,

13:12.320 --> 13:14.790
not only will it ease Mr. Zheng's
so-called inner demons,

13:14.790 --> 13:16.270
but it will also give the major nobles

13:16.270 --> 13:17.930
a satisfactory explanation.

13:17.960 --> 13:20.000
If, in the end,
regarding this repair work,

13:20.000 --> 13:22.290
only a few people appreciate
Fan Yun's favor,

13:22.290 --> 13:23.900
our goal is still achieved.

13:24.600 --> 13:26.410
If Mr. Zheng wants to make another move,

13:26.410 --> 13:27.940
he will have to think twice.

13:28.790 --> 13:29.620
Besides,

13:32.320 --> 13:33.440
if I can use someone else's money,

13:33.440 --> 13:34.770
why should I spend mine?

13:35.840 --> 13:37.150
Then why...

13:42.360 --> 13:43.630
Are you really not worried

13:43.630 --> 13:45.360
about what's going on
between Her Ladyship and Lou Qiyan?

13:45.360 --> 13:46.730
I'm indeed worried.

13:47.040 --> 13:48.040
Worried to death.

14:01.150 --> 14:02.210
It's getting late.

14:02.640 --> 14:03.970
I see you're tired.

14:04.000 --> 14:05.180
Let's call it a day.

14:08.420 --> 14:09.950
No, Young Master Qiyan.

14:09.970 --> 14:10.970
Today,

14:11.000 --> 14:12.460
I must get the blueprints.

14:14.320 --> 14:15.220
Someone said,

14:15.400 --> 14:16.450
I'm not musical at all.

14:16.450 --> 14:17.960
It's a fundamental problem.

14:17.960 --> 14:19.020
We can't rush this.

14:20.600 --> 14:22.200
I-I understand.

14:22.600 --> 14:23.510
But...

14:24.310 --> 14:25.510
let me think about it.

14:25.790 --> 14:27.520
Let me think about it some more.

14:34.850 --> 14:35.830
Young Master Qiyan,

14:35.830 --> 14:37.230
try to imitate this note.

14:59.550 --> 15:00.680
What about this one?

15:08.180 --> 15:09.030
I got it!

15:09.880 --> 15:10.960
Young Master Qiyan,

15:10.960 --> 15:11.820
how about this?

15:12.040 --> 15:12.760
I have

15:12.790 --> 15:14.160
a music score here.

15:14.890 --> 15:16.560
Follow this score

15:16.580 --> 15:17.650
and lower every note

15:17.650 --> 15:18.930
by a half step.

15:50.640 --> 15:51.840
Right, right, right.

16:11.390 --> 16:12.850
Let's stop here for today.

16:14.730 --> 16:15.940
Young Master Qiyan,

16:16.790 --> 16:18.640
you just tuned up,

16:19.200 --> 16:20.600
but why stop practicing?

16:21.140 --> 16:22.450
The sun is about to set.

16:23.470 --> 16:24.390
How about

16:24.410 --> 16:26.070
I escort you back home for now?

16:26.390 --> 16:29.250
I'll definitely deliver
the blueprints tomorrow.

16:29.840 --> 16:30.790
Then tomorrow,

16:31.150 --> 16:31.720
deal?

16:32.600 --> 16:33.200
Deal.

16:35.600 --> 16:37.330
Thank you, Young Master Qiyan.

16:37.670 --> 16:39.070
I should be thanking you.

17:03.150 --> 17:05.400
Although I'm average-looking,

17:05.750 --> 17:08.750
you've peeked at me
over a dozen times on this journey.

17:09.380 --> 17:11.069
Isn't that a bit too much?

17:13.130 --> 17:14.240
I...

17:15.079 --> 17:17.609
Young Master Qiyan,
you're overthinking it.

17:18.650 --> 17:20.609
I'm just curious.

17:20.640 --> 17:22.810
Curious about your attire.

17:22.960 --> 17:25.359
You must be missing
a lot of sleep every day.

17:25.910 --> 17:27.800
For things I consider worth doing,

17:27.800 --> 17:29.160
I never count the cost.

17:32.530 --> 17:34.090
You really go all out.

17:36.330 --> 17:37.770
Young Master Qiyan,

17:37.790 --> 17:40.110
since you are a noble of the Zheng family,

17:40.140 --> 17:42.180
why go through all the trouble

17:42.200 --> 17:44.770
to change your name to run Juyun Pavilion?

17:45.250 --> 17:47.450
You shouldn't be short of money, right?

17:52.090 --> 17:54.160
The Zheng surname is a glorious honor,

17:54.160 --> 17:55.620
but also a heavy shackle.

17:56.960 --> 17:57.880
When I was very young,

17:57.880 --> 17:58.880
I thought

17:59.310 --> 18:00.450
that one day,

18:00.640 --> 18:02.170
I must become someone else.

18:03.550 --> 18:04.580
Unrestrained

18:04.900 --> 18:05.920
and free.

18:10.720 --> 18:12.200
I see.

18:36.560 --> 18:37.210
Have we arrived?

18:37.210 --> 18:38.070
We've arrived.

18:47.200 --> 18:47.890
Well,

18:47.920 --> 18:50.050
why isn't there even a mounting block?

18:53.180 --> 18:54.010
No need.

18:54.040 --> 18:56.170
I... I can do it myself.

19:14.990 --> 19:16.390
Thank you, Young Master.

19:17.920 --> 19:18.620
Then,

19:18.730 --> 19:19.730
see you tomorrow.

19:20.090 --> 19:21.090
See you tomorrow.

19:21.740 --> 19:23.720
I don't think you need
to see each other tomorrow.

19:23.720 --> 19:24.720
Your Excellency.

19:26.300 --> 19:27.430
Why did you come out?

19:29.000 --> 19:30.650
You're so elegant, Your Excellency,

19:30.650 --> 19:33.780
playing the zither at the gate
in the middle of the night.

19:39.030 --> 19:41.810
Isn't this to prevent someone
from pretending to be lost

19:41.810 --> 19:44.410
and not bringing my wife
back to the residence?

19:52.440 --> 19:53.290
Um,

19:53.310 --> 19:54.780
the residence gates are about to close.

19:54.780 --> 19:55.730
Let's go back.

19:55.750 --> 19:56.600
Yes.

19:57.480 --> 19:58.240
Let us

19:58.930 --> 20:00.330
go back to our residence.

20:06.310 --> 20:07.270
Okay.

20:14.230 --> 20:15.540
Um, Young Master Qiyan,

20:15.540 --> 20:17.170
you must give me the blueprints tomorrow.

20:17.170 --> 20:17.850
Remember!

20:17.870 --> 20:18.630
You must!

20:19.980 --> 20:22.040
He promised to give us the blueprints.

20:22.040 --> 20:22.760
Shut up.

20:29.870 --> 20:31.270
Absolutely ridiculous!

20:32.310 --> 20:32.950
Yes.

20:33.160 --> 20:34.750
His Excellency is young and inexperienced.

20:34.750 --> 20:36.480
Please don't be angry, My Lord.

20:36.600 --> 20:37.600
What?

20:38.330 --> 20:41.090
Is His Excellency someone
you can criticize?

20:42.260 --> 20:43.050
Yes.

20:43.250 --> 20:44.490
I know my mistake.

20:49.950 --> 20:51.040
It seems

20:51.060 --> 20:52.300
this Fan Yun

20:52.750 --> 20:54.560
is truly a disaster.

20:58.590 --> 21:00.310
Has Shi returned?

21:01.390 --> 21:02.320
Young Master Shi

21:02.340 --> 21:05.200
is still studying
at the Directorate of Education.

21:07.880 --> 21:09.700
One must marry a virtuous wife.

21:10.680 --> 21:12.030
With His Excellency

21:12.030 --> 21:13.680
as a warning example,

21:15.240 --> 21:16.820
Shi's marriage

21:17.160 --> 21:19.090
needs to be considered carefully.

21:19.870 --> 21:21.070
Young Master Shi

21:21.600 --> 21:24.260
is devoted to his studies
and stays away from women.

21:24.260 --> 21:26.390
Please rest assured, Master.

21:27.550 --> 21:28.550
Furthermore,

21:28.800 --> 21:31.710
using the ancestor's dream as your excuse,

21:31.730 --> 21:34.450
you've thrown His Excellency
into confusion.

22:16.010 --> 22:17.250
Charge!

22:17.270 --> 22:23.180
-Kill!
-Kill!

22:26.840 --> 22:27.750
Grandfather.

22:31.000 --> 22:31.830
Shi,

22:32.430 --> 22:33.270
come here.

22:35.550 --> 22:36.660
Grandfather,

22:36.680 --> 22:38.610
are you feeling better these days?

22:38.960 --> 22:39.920
I found a recipe

22:39.960 --> 22:41.400
for soothing tea

22:41.400 --> 22:42.390
and had the servants brew it.

22:42.390 --> 22:43.260
Try it

22:43.280 --> 22:45.540
and see if it helps ease your nightmares.

22:46.770 --> 22:48.500
That's very thoughtful of you.

22:50.480 --> 22:51.870
Did you just come back

22:52.330 --> 22:54.560
from studying
at the Directorate of Education?

22:54.560 --> 22:55.170
Yes.

22:55.440 --> 22:57.430
I gave this recipe
to the servants before I left.

22:57.430 --> 22:59.880
I brought it from the kitchen
as soon as I got back.

22:59.880 --> 23:00.710
Sit.

23:06.610 --> 23:07.720
My grandson,

23:08.270 --> 23:09.260
you don't need to worry

23:09.260 --> 23:10.700
too much about my health.

23:10.750 --> 23:11.510
Look at you,

23:11.600 --> 23:12.920
having to study

23:12.950 --> 23:14.880
and care for me.

23:15.980 --> 23:17.240
There is nothing wrong

23:17.240 --> 23:18.530
with my health.

23:18.680 --> 23:19.960
Don't worry too much.

23:25.160 --> 23:27.590
While studying at the directorate
these days,

23:27.590 --> 23:29.350
I heard some gossip.

23:29.830 --> 23:31.210
Your illness these days

23:31.550 --> 23:33.680
has greatly affected the Nine Cities.

23:34.700 --> 23:36.150
What did they say?

23:37.310 --> 23:38.480
You hold a high position

23:38.480 --> 23:40.050
as the hub of the Nine Cities,

23:40.050 --> 23:42.250
handling many case procedures.

23:42.270 --> 23:44.690
It might not affect Qi Zheng,
the muddle-headed Governor,

23:44.690 --> 23:46.220
too much.

23:46.370 --> 23:47.340
But...

23:48.210 --> 23:49.810
the people will be affected.

23:53.910 --> 23:55.180
The people.

23:59.540 --> 24:00.690
You asked me that day

24:00.720 --> 24:02.250
if you were a good official.

24:02.280 --> 24:03.140
I was thinking,

24:03.680 --> 24:05.240
if the Nine Cities
didn't have a loyal official

24:05.240 --> 24:06.920
like you who serves the people,

24:06.920 --> 24:08.050
it would be in chaos.

24:09.100 --> 24:09.970
The Governor

24:10.000 --> 24:11.720
ignores state affairs all day.

24:11.720 --> 24:13.650
They say he's been looking for some

24:13.920 --> 24:15.580
ancestral temple these days.

24:17.560 --> 24:18.620
Ancestral temple?

24:19.740 --> 24:21.160
A temple built for dead nobles

24:21.160 --> 24:23.290
after the founding of the Nine Cities.

24:23.380 --> 24:24.940
It's long been abandoned.

24:25.880 --> 24:27.960
I don't know what Qi Zheng is thinking.

24:27.960 --> 24:29.090
He wants to repair it

24:30.370 --> 24:31.570
to pay tribute

24:31.590 --> 24:33.810
to those meritorious officials
of the past.

24:33.810 --> 24:35.340
He also said something like

24:35.880 --> 24:38.810
"never forget their merits
in protecting the city."

24:44.000 --> 24:44.960
It's delicious.

24:45.190 --> 24:46.390
Delicious.

25:01.520 --> 25:03.720
What were you talking about so happily?

25:03.870 --> 25:06.470
You two were reluctant
to part even at the gate.

25:06.590 --> 25:07.400
Your Excellency,

25:07.400 --> 25:09.550
why were you at the gate?

25:10.510 --> 25:11.510
Don't interrupt.

25:12.040 --> 25:13.680
He knew you were my wife,

25:13.700 --> 25:15.240
yet he still touched you.

25:15.880 --> 25:17.940
Isn't this a clear provocation to me?

25:18.310 --> 25:19.240
I'm telling you,

25:19.470 --> 25:20.600
from now on,

25:20.620 --> 25:22.150
you must stay away from him.

25:22.830 --> 25:24.340
This morning,

25:24.510 --> 25:25.640
it was you

25:25.660 --> 25:27.160
who let me out of the residence.

25:27.160 --> 25:27.670
I...

25:28.610 --> 25:29.960
He has promised me.

25:29.980 --> 25:32.240
He will give us the blueprints tomorrow.

25:34.360 --> 25:35.520
If you ask me,

25:36.330 --> 25:38.400
you're so charming now.

25:38.430 --> 25:40.560
Everyone is rushing to give you gifts.

25:42.030 --> 25:43.160
I exhausted

25:43.160 --> 25:44.350
all the skills I have learned in my life

25:44.350 --> 25:45.480
to get it, okay?

25:46.330 --> 25:47.730
You don't know.

25:47.760 --> 25:49.150
Teaching Zheng Shi

25:49.170 --> 25:50.620
to play a song

25:50.930 --> 25:52.860
is harder than climbing to heaven.

25:53.400 --> 25:54.520
Even now,

25:54.720 --> 25:56.440
my back still aches.

25:57.750 --> 25:58.510
All right.

25:59.220 --> 26:00.680
I know you've worked hard.

26:01.170 --> 26:01.960
Then tomorrow,

26:01.960 --> 26:03.760
let Wei and Yan do the handover.

26:03.780 --> 26:04.910
You don't need to go.

26:05.480 --> 26:06.310
Why?

26:06.880 --> 26:07.830
No reason.

26:08.240 --> 26:09.900
I have my own considerations.

26:09.900 --> 26:11.100
Don't worry about it.

26:15.370 --> 26:16.370
Fine, fine.

26:17.070 --> 26:17.960
Anyway,

26:18.720 --> 26:20.140
you use Fan Yun when there is trouble,

26:20.140 --> 26:22.000
and Wei and Yan when there's none.

26:22.150 --> 26:23.320
After all,

26:23.340 --> 26:25.640
you still trust the people
around you more.

26:25.640 --> 26:26.400
Why?

26:27.070 --> 26:28.000
Are you jealous?

26:29.030 --> 26:30.400
It's not jealousy.

26:31.030 --> 26:32.160
It's a lack of trust.

26:42.790 --> 26:43.910
Hurry, hurry.

26:56.300 --> 26:58.100
It seems that in this residence,

26:58.490 --> 27:00.020
except for Second Brother,

27:00.530 --> 27:01.560
no one has ever run around for me

27:01.560 --> 27:02.760
so busily.

27:04.030 --> 27:04.880
This feeling

27:06.420 --> 27:07.740
is long lost.

27:10.440 --> 27:11.550
Since

27:12.240 --> 27:13.880
the one in front of me now

27:14.510 --> 27:15.470
is the real you,

27:18.000 --> 27:19.070
why don't you...

27:19.800 --> 27:20.730
Why don't I what?

27:21.680 --> 27:22.510
Why don't you

27:23.070 --> 27:25.040
talk about
your selection exam reform plan?

27:25.040 --> 27:25.910
Okay?

27:30.650 --> 27:32.040
Do you really want to know?

27:32.040 --> 27:33.150
Of course.

27:39.830 --> 27:41.480
Since you are so nice,

27:42.090 --> 27:44.090
I can tell you about it.

27:44.470 --> 27:45.470
Can women

27:45.500 --> 27:47.610
also take the exam?

27:49.350 --> 27:50.030
To take...

27:51.100 --> 27:52.290
take a step back,

27:53.070 --> 27:54.800
even if women can take the exam,

27:54.860 --> 27:55.780
you can't.

27:57.910 --> 27:59.190
I can't?

28:09.020 --> 28:11.210
Lord Lyu's 500 gold

28:12.890 --> 28:15.130
is getting less and less worthwhile.

28:17.840 --> 28:18.600
Wait.

28:19.690 --> 28:21.640
What did you say about 500 gold?

28:43.630 --> 28:45.030
Let me ask you a question.

28:45.720 --> 28:47.070
What do you think of me?

28:55.770 --> 28:57.240
Why is everyone so quiet?

28:58.400 --> 28:59.810
With such quality,

28:59.920 --> 29:01.110
it's only worth 500 gold?

29:01.110 --> 29:02.710
Don't you think it's absurd?

29:05.240 --> 29:05.900
Never mind.

29:10.320 --> 29:11.320
Ultimately,

29:12.820 --> 29:14.580
I am just a business deal.

29:20.480 --> 29:22.870
Why didn't my wife come to greet me today?

29:24.110 --> 29:25.320
Her Ladyship

29:25.790 --> 29:27.720
was probably exhausted last night,

29:27.720 --> 29:29.120
so she is still sleeping.

29:29.400 --> 29:30.330
Still sleeping?

29:31.480 --> 29:32.850
What time is it now?

29:34.510 --> 29:36.240
Your Ladyship. Your Ladyship.

29:47.960 --> 29:49.610
Qiuyue.

29:59.640 --> 30:01.380
What are you doing here?

30:01.590 --> 30:03.020
-We were ordered
-We were ordered

30:03.020 --> 30:06.400
-to wake you up, Your Ladyship.
-to wake you up, Your Ladyship.

30:06.400 --> 30:07.440
Wake me up?

30:07.990 --> 30:08.790
But...

30:09.660 --> 30:11.550
what time is it now?

30:11.580 --> 30:12.640
-Your Ladyship,
-Your Ladyship,

30:12.640 --> 30:13.970
-it's dawn.
-it's dawn.

30:14.590 --> 30:15.640
Dawn?

30:16.830 --> 30:17.830
That's strange.

30:18.640 --> 30:19.680
Why is my neck

30:20.470 --> 30:21.990
so sore?

31:12.310 --> 31:13.260
If you ask me,

31:14.830 --> 31:16.050
lacking exercise

31:16.200 --> 31:19.170
is the main reason why she feels
more tired after sleeping.

31:19.170 --> 31:19.880
Wei Zhu.

31:20.200 --> 31:21.730
Go and wake her up right now.

31:22.110 --> 31:22.730
Today,

31:23.110 --> 31:24.750
arrange horse riding, cuju,
and fifteen-pin bowling

31:24.750 --> 31:26.040
for her.

31:26.510 --> 31:28.170
Not a single one can be missed.

31:31.030 --> 31:31.830
Qiuyue,

31:32.130 --> 31:33.200
what are they

31:33.240 --> 31:34.170
doing here?

31:34.190 --> 31:35.050
Your Ladyship,

31:35.430 --> 31:36.960
for some reason, His Excellency

31:36.960 --> 31:37.880
has arranged a lot of

31:37.880 --> 31:39.540
physical activities for you.

31:39.880 --> 31:41.740
But the sun is so scorching today.

31:41.950 --> 31:42.670
I am

31:42.750 --> 31:44.420
afraid you might get heatstroke.

31:44.420 --> 31:46.740
His Excellency arranged it for me?

31:52.590 --> 31:53.650
It doesn't matter.

31:53.960 --> 31:55.110
I love these

31:55.110 --> 31:56.730
physical activities the most.

31:56.730 --> 31:57.340
Come on,

31:57.960 --> 31:59.290
help me change clothes.

32:10.870 --> 32:13.900
-Great!
-Great!

32:14.340 --> 32:15.510
Zheng Yuan was previously

32:15.510 --> 32:16.840
plagued by nightmares.

32:17.270 --> 32:18.330
He kept dreaming of

32:19.000 --> 32:21.400
the meritorious officials
who died in battle.

32:21.400 --> 32:23.270
I remember when the late governor
built the city,

32:23.270 --> 32:24.310
he specially built an ancestral temple

32:24.310 --> 32:26.000
for the meritorious officials.

32:26.000 --> 32:26.660
Therefore,

32:27.200 --> 32:28.730
I plan to rebuild the temple

32:28.790 --> 32:30.050
and start worshiping,

32:30.420 --> 32:31.400
to commemorate

32:31.920 --> 32:32.790
the nobles who made

32:32.790 --> 32:35.050
great contributions to the Nine Cities.

32:37.750 --> 32:38.480
Next one.

32:49.740 --> 32:52.790
The Governor of the Nine Cities
is only worth 500 gold.

32:52.810 --> 32:55.340
One month of purchase
equals half of my worth.

32:55.550 --> 32:56.260
Rejected.

32:57.480 --> 32:59.810
The budget must be reduced
by at least 30%.

33:01.040 --> 33:03.970
Repairing the villa costs
twice as much as I'm worth.

33:06.000 --> 33:06.600
Rejected.

33:07.220 --> 33:07.980
Next one.

33:08.000 --> 33:08.980
Next round.

33:09.230 --> 33:10.560
Where is the next round?

33:12.020 --> 33:13.530
Keep up, those falling behind!

33:13.530 --> 33:14.570
Hurry!

33:27.830 --> 33:28.760
I'm exhausted.

33:36.640 --> 33:37.570
Rejected.

33:46.400 --> 33:47.430
Next one.

33:47.700 --> 33:48.660
Where is it?

33:50.990 --> 33:51.610
Let's go.

33:51.480 --> 34:02.960
[Taiji Palace]

33:56.210 --> 33:59.810
What was wrong with His Excellency
at the morning meeting today?

33:59.930 --> 34:01.530
He was kicking everyone out.

34:03.160 --> 34:04.550
It's only natural for him
to lose his temper

34:04.550 --> 34:06.280
when he hasn't had enough rest.

34:15.320 --> 34:16.320
Your Excellency.

34:17.070 --> 34:18.070
Your Excellency.

34:20.460 --> 34:21.860
Why are you in such a rush?

34:21.960 --> 34:23.090
What's the urgency?

34:24.400 --> 34:25.199
You tell him.

34:27.150 --> 34:28.150
Your Excellency,

34:28.830 --> 34:31.230
Yan Jiang and I just
went to Juyun Pavilion,

34:31.310 --> 34:32.440
but we were shut out.

34:33.880 --> 34:34.739
What happened?

34:36.040 --> 34:36.850
This Zheng Shi

34:37.320 --> 34:38.100
is so bold.

34:38.630 --> 34:40.070
He didn't even see us,

34:40.090 --> 34:40.929
saying that

34:41.239 --> 34:43.320
he'll only trade with Her Ladyship alone

34:43.320 --> 34:44.780
and won't see anyone else.

34:46.840 --> 34:48.150
How dare Zheng Shi!

34:49.139 --> 34:50.659
Her Ladyship has arrived!

34:51.270 --> 34:52.980
W-Where is His Excellency?

34:54.040 --> 34:54.940
Your Excellency,

34:54.940 --> 34:55.909
why did you

34:55.940 --> 34:58.200
arrange so many activities for me today?

34:58.800 --> 34:59.800
You all may leave.

35:03.810 --> 35:04.850
Hurry up and go.

35:09.460 --> 35:10.900
With Her Ladyship's attitude just now,

35:10.900 --> 35:12.410
what if they really fight?

35:12.430 --> 35:13.310
We have to go back.

35:13.310 --> 35:14.270
Go back?

35:15.880 --> 35:16.800
Why?

35:17.510 --> 35:18.760
To break up the fight.

35:20.020 --> 35:21.550
You always want to show off.

35:21.650 --> 35:22.780
Go back if you want.

35:22.810 --> 35:24.140
I won't be a third wheel.

35:25.860 --> 35:26.660
No.

35:28.400 --> 35:29.660
I'm telling you, we...

35:31.980 --> 35:32.620
Wei Ying!

35:33.330 --> 35:34.040
Wei Ying!
